  "comment": "Pixbar - BAR224FXL - 53 channel: The BAR224FXL uses 224x SMD RGB 3-in-1 LEDs to produce a powerful party effect. With onboard modes and DMX control, you can utilise the 16 segment control to create visual effects. \n\nLight Source: 224x SMD 5050 RGB LEDs\nBeam Angle: 90°\nPWM: 10,000 Hz\nOperation Modes: DMX, auto, manual, sound active, master/slave\nControl Interface: 3-pin XLR in/out\nDMX Channels: 3/5/8/24/48/53\nInput Voltage: 110-240V AC, 50/60 Hz\nDimensions: 1100x60x60 mm\nWeight: 3.5 kg",
